SeriesDescription: Proportion of electronic waste collected (%)
Source: Instituto Nacional de Estadstica y Censos (INEC)
FootNote: The data contained in these cells correspond to the amount of cell phones recovered (units), through the application of ministerial agreement 191. The data is shown in units and is currently the only electronic waste of which there is an annual record. The registry of monthly declarations by the producers and their respective annual sum is attached. The report is given in units based on national regulations. The generation information was taken from the consultancy carried out for the development of the technical standard for waste management of electrical-electronic devices. These data were taken from the United Nations study for the estimation of waste generation of electric-electronic devices in Latin America.
